claim.claim-text:
The recording apparatus according to Claim 4 further comprising:
a main body frame (50) that is arranged in the main apparatus body;
other substrates (93) that are controlled by the substrate (70);
a connector (76) that is mounted on the substrate to be connected to a wiring (65) between the substrate and the other substrates; and
a lateral plate section (54a) that extends from the main body frame to be arranged on an outside of the power transmission mechanism (59) in the width direction (X) in the mechanical component arrangement area (MA),
wherein the wiring (65) which includes one end section connected to the connector (76) is wired on a surface of the lateral plate section (54a) opposite to the power transmission mechanism (59), and configured to include the other end section connected to the other substrates.
